A new "Master PDF" feature allows for the generation of all payslips for a specific payroll run into a single, multi-page document.

- **One-Click Batching**: Generates a unified PDF from the current payroll period with entity branding.
- **Itemized Layout**: Includes detailed breakdowns for earnings and deductions as per MOM requirements.

